  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypertensive haemodialysis patients are at high risk for cardiovascular events. This study
      was undertaken to ascertain whether the upstream of aliskirne, a direct renin inhibitor
      improves mortality and cardiovascular outcomes in these high-risk population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
